<h3 style="padding-top: 2em;">Cages and Addons</h3>

<div class="table table-100">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-2">
            <img src="~/lib/Images/DungeonPetz/ExperimentalCage.png" style="width: 100px;" />
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-8">
            <ul style="margin: 0; padding: 0">
                <li>May double 1 symbol to reduce the others to 0</li>
                <li>May make different choice each round</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="table-row" style="padding-top: 3em;">
            <div class="table-cell tc-2">
                <img src="~/lib/Images/DungeonPetz/GoesDing.png" style="width: 100px;" />
            </div>
            <div class="table-cell tc-8">
                <ul style="margin: 0; padding: 0">
                    <li>after evaluating all needs, pay 1 gold to remove 1 suffering and/or 1 mutation</li>
                    <li>may pay to use once per round</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="table-row" style="padding-top: 3em;">
            <div class="table-cell tc-2">
                <img src="~/lib/Images/DungeonPetz/Jukebox.png" style="width: 100px;" />
            </div>
            <div class="table-cell tc-8">
                <ul style="margin: 0; padding: 0">
                    <li>starts empty</li>
                    <li>before evaluating needs in phase 4, may pay to change token</li>
                    <li>may pay to move token once per round</li>
                    <li>effect continues indefinitely</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
